  <div class="container">
    <header>
      <h1>Visa-Free Countries Checker</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Select your passport nationality and instantly see which countries you can visit <strong>visa-free</strong>, with <strong>visa on arrival</strong>, <strong>eVisa</strong>, or <strong>visa required</strong>.</p>
    </header>

    <!-- Intro -->
    <section>
      <div class="prose">
        <p>Planning international travel starts with one question: <strong>where can I go with my passport?</strong> This <strong>visa-free countries checker</strong> shows your travel access for 50+ popular destinations worldwide. Select your passport below to see a color-coded breakdown of <strong>visa-free destinations</strong>, visa-on-arrival options, eVisa countries, and places that require a full visa application.</p>
        <p>Data reflects <strong>2026 visa policies</strong> for the 30 most common passport nationalities. Always confirm current requirements with official government sources before booking travel.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

